title: Production of new motor vehicles in Canada 2016
summary: Chart shows the Production of shipment motor in Canada the Year 2016 .
We have a chart depicting dollar Production on a Month over scale .
With a lot of volatility int he starting months then a slight plateau in the summer months , approaching the winter months we have a dip but then a rocket highs for the end of the year .
gold: A Graph showing the production of new motor vehicles by Canada in 2016 . As you can see the production had a big climbing in Q1 2016 . It stayed stable in Q2 and Q3 , while fell down in Q4 .
